{
	"_readme": "V21 preregistered compute-matched solo self-imitation control, initialized from the first reach-30 critic seed at generation 10. It collects and forwards the identical phase-balanced winning-episode replay as treatment but multiplies its masked chosen-action loss by zero. Pair with fair-v21-solo-sil-treatment005; every causal setting other than selfImitation.coef, output root, and this note is identical. No solo checkpoint is promotion-eligible without held-out multiplayer, heuristic, exploiter, and human gates.",
